replies.bodyText:
I've updated to the approach below.  Similar to what you suggested, but matches other similar methods on this Builder a bit better.
        public Builder authRules(@NonNull List<AuthRule> authRules) {
            Objects.requireNonNull(authRules);
            this.authRules.clear();
            this.authRules.addAll(authRules);
            return this;
        }

